proxmox

base domain 	        - dc=ldap,dc=goauthentik,dc=io
user attribute 	        - sAMAccountName
group name attribute    - cn
bindDN 			        - cn=akadmin,ou=users,dc=ldap,dc=goauthentik,dc=io
server 			        - idp.cloud.lab
user filter		        - (&(memberOf=cn=private_cloud_users,ou=groups,dc=ldap,dc=goauthentik,dc=io))
group filter	        - leave this empty